Trust Her Webmap Trust Her webmap for internal use only. Webmap contains toggle selections in order to turn various datasets on or off dependent on need. Trust Her Clinics: Locations of current Trust Her clinics based on location and clinic system. Car Travel Time: Raster layer visualizing the average travel time to a Trust Her clinic within a 15 minute drive time. Women (15 to 49): Census tracts layer visualizing women of reproductive age (between 15 to 49 years old) across Dallas County. DART Bus: Locations of DART bus stops across Dallas County. DART Rail: Locations of DART rail stations across Dallas County.
